{"text":"48. Va yerni to`shab qo`ydik. \nBiz qandoq ham yaxshi tayyorlovchidirmiz!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,72]}]}

{"text":"49. Va Biz har bir narsani juft yaratdik. \nShoyadki, eslasangizlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,67]}]}

{"text":"50. Bas, faqat Allohgagina qoching. \nAlbatta, men sizlarga Undan (kelgan) \nochiq-oydin ogohlantiruvchiman.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,106]}]}

{"text":"51. Va Allohga boshqa ma'budni sherik qilmanglar. {"text":"52. Xuddi shunday, bulardan avvalgilarga ham har bir Payg`ambar kelgan vaqt (uni) sehrgar yoki majnun deganlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,111]}]}

{"text":"53. Kelishib olganmilar?! \nYo`q, ular tug`yonga ketgan qavmlardir!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,66]}]}

{"text":"54. Ulardan yuz o`gir. \nBas, sen malomatga qoluvchi emassan.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,60]}]}

{"text":"55. Va eslatgin. \nAlbatta, eslatish mo`minlarga manfaat berur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,62]}]}

{"text":"59.
